    "data": [
        {
            "title": "天文台｜今日能見低有驟雨  市區氣溫最高約29度 明日降至約17度",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/2a117edea1cf6e76d3fad9b1c1245715/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032807492381954.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>天文台表示，現時位於華南北部的一道冷鋒會在今日（28日）移近華南沿岸。本港今日有幾陣驟雨，日間短暫時間有陽光及炎熱，下午稍後局部地區亦可能有雷暴。隨著冷鋒在今晚橫過沿岸地區，受隨後的東北季候風影響，市區氣溫會於今日稍後由最高約29度顯著下降至星期六（29日）約17度，新界再低兩三度。由於在一日左右時間降溫顯著，市民請留意天氣變化，注意保暖。\n\n</p>\n<p>一股偏南氣流正影響廣東沿岸，本港今早能見度頗低，港內的能見度降至2000米左右，而橫瀾島的能見度更降至500米以下。此外，預料現時位於華南北部的一道冷鋒會在今晚橫過沿岸地區。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162832/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"本港今早能見度頗低。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6694184c84d72792e4dcf915c50ea04b/2025-03/44.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        本港今早能見度頗低。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162830/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e782a6ed917f8520c379e113bdeb14c6/2025-03/Screenshot_2025-03-27_at_11_43_21_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162831/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4f9cbb76c142360aab1144001b3e51e3/2025-03/Screenshot_2025-03-27_at_11_43_44_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162833/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"本港今日能見度頗低。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8ed1305916bc6e3d667ce2a8508318cd/2025-03/45.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        本港今日能見度頗低。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4162834/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/90b007e90ebd7f6b50b4aa0c84799cd3/2025-03/47.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>天文台又指，今日大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。初時能見度頗低，吹輕微至和緩偏南風，下午稍後局部地區可能有雷暴，今晚轉吹和緩至清勁東北風，氣溫下降至午夜最低約<b>21</b>度。\n\n</p>\n<p>展望週末至下週初早晚清涼，市區最低氣溫在<b>16</b>度左右，新界再低兩三度。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
